This is boiler-plate code for an open-world first-person shooter game.

Vision: Provide first-person shooter roleplaying gameplay similar to the recent
installments of The Elder Scrolls and Fallout series, albeit with the addition of 
couch-multiplayer coop.

Current version: 0.0.2

    Current features
Menus(Inventory)
Input(In-Game)
Actor(Movement, Item Interaction, condition(health))
Items(charging, pickup, drop, use)
Inventory(store)
Abilities(Dual-wield, Unarmed, fireball, heal)

    Pending features for 1.0.0
Menus(Main, Save&Load, Options, Speech, Trade, Quest)
Input(Menu)
Actor(XP/RPG Stats, Combat AI, Ambient AI, condition(fatigue, mana, stat mods, effects&perks))
Items(Warp door, shield type, thrown type, damage&repair, ranged melee, containers)
Inventory(Looting);
Save&Load(Starting Map, interior cells, exterior cells , PlayerData)
World(Interior cells, exterior cells, NPC placement)
Speech(speech tree, Trade system)
Quest(Quest)

What needs to be done for 0.1.0 (Base FPS Gameplay)

Actor(Combat AI)
Items(shield type, thrown type, ranged melee)
